reviewText: It is an old movie.  Needs to be updated.

No, I do not hate it as the star rating suggest. In stead, I like it that the information it provides. I like it because it brings me where I might not have time to go. maybe, the star rating system got to go! Nice scenery though!
Wonderful book!  I really enjoyed all the beautiful pictures with the trains and the scenery.  A friend showed me this book and I had to have it.
This is a very well produced DVD. Brings back all the fun i had travelling on the "Canadian" from Vancouver to Jasper.
